    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚反垄断机构警告采取措施遏制价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/nigerian-antitrust-body-warns-of-steps-to-curb-escalating-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚反垄断机构表示，尽管奈拉近期走强，但仍将采取措施抑制价格持续上涨。]]></description>
