    <item>
      <title>米其林挑战欧盟寻找轮胎卡特尔证据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/michelin-challenges-eu-s-hunt-for-evidence-of-tire-cartel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着监管机构席卷整个轮胎行业，寻找涉嫌垄断价格卡特尔的证据，米其林正在挑战欧盟对其设施进行反垄断搜查的合法性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/michelin-challenges-eu-s-hunt-for-evidence-of-tire-cartel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:03:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员提出禁止算法稳定币的新法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/senators-tout-new-stablecoin-bill-as-broader-banking-deal-eyed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位参议员——一名共和党人，一名民主党人——在众议院和参议院推动最快下个月通过此类立法的过程中，正在提出一项监管稳定币的措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/senators-tout-new-stablecoin-bill-as-broader-banking-deal-eyed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列和伊朗紧张局势加剧，沙特和阿联酋警告战争危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/saudis-and-uae-warn-of-war-dangers-as-israel-iran-tensions-boil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯和阿拉伯联合酋长国周三在一份异常坦率的联合声明中呼吁中东地区实行最大限度的“自我克制”，以使该地区“免受战争危险及其可怕后果”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/saudis-and-uae-warn-of-war-dangers-as-israel-iran-tensions-boil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:48:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚副总理下令将纳吉布软禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/malaysia-s-najib-has-witness-supporting-his-house-arrest-request</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚副总理艾哈迈德·扎希德·哈米迪表示，他看到前总理纳吉布·拉扎克软禁中服完与 1MDB 相关的剩余刑期的命令，并支持后者在司法审查中的主张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/malaysia-s-najib-has-witness-supporting-his-house-arrest-request</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:22:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰里米·亨特表示降息将提振英国情绪，暗示秋季投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/hunt-says-rate-cuts-would-lift-uk-mood-hints-at-fall-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特表示，今年晚些时候降息的前景将提振选民的情绪，并暗示首相苏纳克要到秋季才会举行大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/hunt-says-rate-cuts-would-lift-uk-mood-hints-at-fall-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 18:38:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
